<section class="bg-off-white py-20 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center lg:gap-20 lg:px-8">
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl">
      <img
        src="/images/team/mene-avatar.png"
        alt="Mene Demestihas, Founder & CEO of Metrias Medical"
        width="600"
        height="600"
        class="h-auto w-full object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-[32px] leading-tight font-bold text-black md:text-[44px] md:leading-tight">
        Physician founded, built for Operators
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-6 font-body text-lg leading-relaxed text-payer-slate">
        Dr. Mene Demestihas saw the discharge bottleneck firsthand — patients waiting hours
        for paperwork while beds sat occupied and ERs backed up. The problem wasn't clinical.
        It was administrative.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 font-body text-lg leading-relaxed text-payer-slate">
        He founded Metrias Medical to solve it with the same rigor physicians bring
        to patient care: deploy skilled experts, arm them with purpose-built software,
        and let the data teach the system to get faster over time.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4">
        <div>
          <p class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-black">
            Mene Demestihas, MD
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-base text-payer-slate">
            Founder & CEO
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
